displayName: Lasra Forest - In front of the Cave

parameters: HP. MP has been fully restored.
"Oh my, you took quite a while to arrive."

"Dyuhh, could it be that you're trying to prolong the
mission because you want to spend more time with me?"

"Dyuhuhu, please don't glare at me like that. Didn't we
share such love yesterday?"

"Well, no matter. Shall we head to the cave that's our
objective right away?"
"(He's insisting on completing the request, huh.)"

"(If the purpose was to brainwash me, there would be no need
to complete the request.)"

"(He could just use the full time to keep me confined in
this rest area for training.)"

"(And yet he's going out of his way to complete the request,
which means...)"

"(According to the contract of servitude, I must act to
complete the request or it would be considered non-
fulfillment.)"

"(In other words, unless I myself am convinced that I am
undertaking the request, it would be a breach of contract.)"
"(Or perhaps, he has set a trap ahead to ensnare me.)"

"(Well, either way, I have no choice but to head towards the
cave...)"

"Yes, of course I'm going. I want to get this request over
with quickly."
"But before that, I'll give something a try."

Without any initial motion and with a speed invisible to the
eye, Tina strikes at Maroges.

Before Tina's blade could reach Maroges, it slowed down, and
Tina fell to the ground.

"Oh dear, how frightening. To suddenly strike at your
employer."

"The spell of a brainwashed slave is designed so that if you
rebel, you won't be able to muster any strength until I
permit it."

"(Damn, I thought he might have taken precautions against
attacks, but to think I wouldn't even be able to stand...)"

Maroges touches Tina's body and chants something, and
strength returns to Tina's body.

"Fuhii, now do you understand? The only thing you can do,
Tina-san, is to complete the request."

"Hmph, if you behave yourself, this will be over before you
know it."

"(For now, since I have no means of overcoming this, I have
no choice but to obey.)"

"(On top of that, I'll have to try every method I can think
of one by one to find a weakness.)"
Tina: "Let's get moving. For the sake of blasting you away."
Maroges probably understands what Tina is thinking.

Still, the fact that Maroges has the upper hand speaks
volumes about the difficulty of breaking this situation.
